A teacher of Government Secondary School (GSS), Kuje, Abuja Mrs. Daramola Matina has been abducted by gunmen. The Nation gathered that the incident occurred at Shadadi community in Kuje Local Council on Tuesday when the armed men invaded the area. A source close to the victim said the suspected kidnappers stormed the area, targeting only the teacher. When contacted by our correspondent, the FCT police spokesman Maryam Yusuf, confirmed the incident. According to the PPRO, the FCT Police Command has launched an operation to ensure the victim is rescued unhurt.